WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:08.408 --> 00:00:12.178
 Subtitles: Kumbol :: WoWCenter.pl :: 

00:00:41.187 --> 00:00:43.083
 He is thirsty. 

00:00:43.959 --> 00:00:46.314
 Take them to the waters. 

00:00:59.769 --> 00:01:01.112
 Enough! 

00:01:01.826 --> 00:01:07.086
 You're going crazy for too long, Hellscream. 

00:01:07.512 --> 00:01:10.616
 It's time to put an end to it. 

00:01:12.587 --> 00:01:18.813
 Get out of my way, pandarenia. You are facing a force that you do not understand. 

00:01:18.992 --> 00:01:23.259
 Your father was entertaining himself with power that he did not understand. 

00:01:23.902 --> 00:01:26.315
 Where is he ... now? 

00:01:57.655 --> 00:02:02.146
 I fought alongside trolls, tauren and other races. 

00:02:02.572 --> 00:02:05.121
 You do not remind them anything. 

00:02:09.139 --> 00:02:14.330
 They are no longer part of my Horde! 

00:02:19.834 --> 00:02:23.673
 The world will know about it. 

00:02:24.801 --> 00:02:27.489
 They will come for you. 

00:02:27.699 --> 00:02:31.398
 Yes ... I'm counting on it. 

00:02:33.079 --> 00:02:36.859
 The armies of the world will come for me. 

00:02:37.705 --> 00:02:44.113
 In the walls of my stronghold, I will oppose them all the horrors I have accumulated. 

00:02:45.037 --> 00:02:49.317
 The boundless power that I have mastered. 

00:02:50.140 --> 00:02:55.921
 One by one they are dying at my feet. 

00:02:56.505 --> 00:03:01.955
 Anyone who stands against my new Horde, 

00:03:02.039 --> 00:03:07.730
 will be pounded on Orgrimmar's spiers! 

00:03:09.099 --> 00:03:15.013
 You pandareni try to tame your hatred and anger, 

00:03:15.388 --> 00:03:19.641
 but such power can not be stopped. 

00:03:19.955 --> 00:03:23.752
 You must free her! 

00:03:29.427 --> 00:03:36.521
 There will come a moment in which you will answer for your crimes. 

00:03:37.152 --> 00:03:42.452
 I do not answer ... to anyone! 

00:03:55.360 --> 00:04:03.724
 Everyone who challenges me will burn in the heat of my hatred ... 

00:04:04.653 --> 00:04:10.016
 Patch 5.4: Siege of Orgrimmar 

00:04:10.695 --> 00:04:13.431
